# Cortex landing-page images.
#
# logo.png is the app icon (already here). Drop these screenshots beside it to
# fill the gallery (16:9 PNGs look best). They reuse the app README's names, so
# you can copy the same files from mind-palace/docs/images/:
#
#   graph-3d.png         — the 3D semantic knowledge graph
#   chat-charts.png      — chat answer with an inline chart + code
#   studio-ide.png       — Cortex Studio IDE
#   document-studio.png  — the Quill document editor
#   deep-research.png     — Deep Research streaming a report
#   generative.png       — Generative Studio (PDF / PPTX / CSV)
#   cookbook.png         — hardware-aware Model Cookbook
#
# Until a screenshot exists its tile shows an empty dark panel — harmless.
